snippet.title: Trash Factory - Help the Trash Pandas (raccoons) in this wacky fun trash sorting game.
snippet.description:
Trash Factory is a wacky fun trash sorting game!
Match the items to their corresponding bins based on their colors!
Do not let the manager get angry or you might lose your job!
Help the trash pandas (raccoons) 🦝 sort garbage by making sure the items go to the corresponding trash bins! 🚮
Why? They are trash pandas, and it's your job! 👷
If you don't sort correctly, your manager will get mad and you will lose your job! 😱
The gameplay starts out slow, but gets faster as you do well at your job! (We believe in your abilities!)
Think of this game as a kind of Tetris, but with trash, conveyor belts, and raccoons with hard hats!
